Age model based on IntCal13 calibration curve. Because the sediment below 950 cm is a 'trash' zone that was deposited very rapidly, only the two dates slightly older than the bottommost sediment date are used.

Bacon command line:
Bacon('STEEL',thick=10,acc.mean=10,d.max=1168,depths.file=TRUE)

Bacon settings file:
0 #d.min
1168 #d.max
1 #d.by
1 #depths.file
NA #slump
10 #acc.mean
1.5 #acc.shape
0.7 #mem.mean
4 #mem.strength
NA #hiatus.depths
1000 #hiatus.mean
1 #hiatus.shape
0 #BCAD
1 #cc
0 #postbomb
IntCal13 #cc1
Marine13 #cc2
SHCal13 #cc3
ConstCal #cc4
cm #unit
0 #normal
3 #t.a
4 #t.b
0 #d.R
0 #d.STD
0.95 #prob
